            {
                "code": "// Fork of \"Triangulated Actors\" by wyatt. https://shadertoy.com/view/tltSW8\n// 2020-02-14 04:50:44\n\nMain {\n    vec4 bb = B(U), cc = C(U), dd = D(U),\n         a = A(bb.xy), b = A(cc.xy);\n    float s = sign(bb.x-0.5*R.x);\n    vec4 col = vec4(s,-0.5*s,-s,1);\n    float r = 8.;\n    if (bb.y>0.4*R.y) {r*=1.5;col=vec4(0.8,1,0,1);}\n    \n    float l = length(U-a.xy),\n        j = smoothstep(r,r-1.,l);\n   \tQ = vec4(j)*col;//*max(0.6+0.4*sin(.3+(.1*cc.x/R.x+cc.y+1./(1.+10.*length(dd.zw))*vec4(1,2,3,4))),0.);\n\tfloat o = smoothstep(2.,0.,sg(U,a.xy,b.xy));\n    Q = 5.*Q*o*(1.-o);\n    //Q += smoothstep(2.,1.,mp(U,a.xy,b.xy)*length(a.xy-b.xy));\n}",
